Overview

This dashboard shows the deep security overview related to the Trend Micro Integration.

This dashboard is made to provide general statistics and show the detection of various ingested events.

It provides information about the event by action and and distribution of events by the severity. It also displays event over hostname and host ID. It displays top source IPs and top destination IPs seen on the event. Furthermore, it also shows the distribution of events by category and event code.
